  "body": "The spec mentions: A validator should create and broadcast the attestation halfway through the slot during which the validator is assigned -- that is SLOT_DURATION * 0.5 seconds after the start of slot.\r\n\r\nUpon creating an attestation, the validator should wait until the time hits half of the duration between slots to submit it to the beacon node for broadcasting. We should implement this in the validator client's runner.go file.",
